<!-- HOME -->
<section id="home" class="page active">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Welcome to the Digital Health Record Management System</h2>
      <p style="line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px">
       This portal is a community-driven initiative to protect the health and wellbeing of migrant workers in Kerala. Many workers face challenges like frequent relocations, language barriers, and lack of proper medical documentation — making it harder to receive continuous healthcare.


Our platform provides a secure and centralized digital health record for every worker. With it, healthcare providers can quickly access medical history, perform timely checkups, and ensure workers receive the right treatment when needed.


The system also aligns with the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals:

 
  SDG 3 – Good Health & Wellbeing: Ensuring equal access to quality healthcare for all.

  SDG 10 – Reduced Inequalities: Supporting vulnerable migrant communities and closing healthcare gaps.


By digitizing medical information, we make healthcare accessible, reliable, and portable — no matter where a worker travels. Together, we can improve preventive care, reduce health risks, and safeguard the dignity of Kerala’s migrant workforce
      </p>
      <button class="btn" onclick="showPage('login')">Login</button>
      <button class="btn secondary" onclick="showPage('register')">Register</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

